data.title: Wikidata:Events/Dubai/Open data edit
data.text:
A datathon planned to improve Wikidata content related to United Arab Emirates and Arabic on this International Open Data Day in 2020. This online event is organized to celebrate Open Data Day 2020 and contribute more data to Wikidata.

The datathon plans to improve labels, descriptions and aliases on items, and

Improving statements, values and its qualifiers of items.

If you would like to take part in this datathon, feel free to add your name below.

--Akbarali (talk)

March 7, Open Data Day 2020 – March 8, International Women's Day

There are about 151 human settlements listed in wikidata as human settlements in the UAE which do not have names in Arabic.So we would like to give Arabic names for those human settlement areas.

You can click in this page and edit your content.

This list is periodically updated by a bot. Manual changes to the list will be removed on the next update!
